{"tid":1990161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要細心睇限聚令","createTime":"2020-04-26T13:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T13:16:35.000Z","uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af641126308203d5387d5937dfb86919346657ee","tid":1990161,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RuWA3w0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRuWA3w0.png&h=8473cd97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599G!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap599G%21zh-Hant-HK&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4APtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=09f07208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599G!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要細心睇下條法例，好多野好易中召。<br />\n<br />\n在符合以下條件的情況下，獲授權人員可要求在公眾地方進行的聚集解散 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)該人員合理地相信，該聚集屬受禁羣組聚集<br />\n<br />\n而班狗有權要求擁有、控制或營運該地方的人 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)交出該人所管有的、關乎在該地方進行的任何活動(該人員合理地相信屬受禁羣組聚集者)的任何文件或物品；或<br />\n(ii)提交該人所管有的、關乎上述活動的任何資料。<br />\n<br />\n即係CCTV都會被狗拎去查。仲話要商場聚集...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c372726e0fbabdb9a51041a847b42f088cac0537","tid":1990161,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 乜地方都入得喎"},{"pid":"467ce23e1183b716eb6175add08bb57562f12585","tid":1990161,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"預呢條法例變戒嚴令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}